course_title: Practical Aspects of Anesthesia Practice II
course_description: This course discusses practical issues pertaining to the anesthesiologist assistant and the practice of anesthesia. Covered topics include: licensing and credentialing, medical coding and billing, healthcare financing and delivery systems, and career and leadership opportunities.
